title: Australia's "gun control very different to the United States": Turnbull
text:
Australia's "gun control very different to the United States": Turnbull Friday, February 23, 2018 - 02:00 
Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull says his country's gun laws that were put in place after a mass shooting in Tasmania in 1996 are ''very different to the United States.'' Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
